00:26:18.528 --> 00:26:23.737
iz men getrotn iber toyte mentshn oyf di shveln, zey hobn nit gekent aribergeyn di shveln.

00:26:23.895 --> 00:26:26.319
fun vos iz geven un ven un ver?

00:26:26.493 --> 00:26:28.512
m'hot gehat eygene tsores.

00:26:29.227 --> 00:26:31.331
m'iz aleyn koym gekrokhn.

00:26:33.935 --> 00:26:35.870
tsi gedenkt ir di nemen

00:26:36.146 --> 00:26:40.730
vi hobn geheysn etlekhe ofitsirn, di daytshishe oder di litvinishe?

00:26:40.280 --> 00:26:42.513
NO, ver hot gevust?

00:26:42.558 --> 00:26:43.346
NAH.

00:26:44.347 --> 00:26:47.767
m'hot nit gege-, m'hot dokh nit gekent reydn afile mit zey.

00:26:48.633 --> 00:26:51.935
zey flegn aroysfirn oyfn apel.

00:26:52.059 --> 00:26:53.049
APPEAL.

00:26:56.210 --> 00:26:59.141
flegn aroysfirn oyfn APPEAL.

00:27:00.311 --> 00:27:04.575
flegt men oysrufn di nemen, un dos iz geven di gantse APPEAL.

00:27:05.357 --> 00:27:08.777
hot men zikh gefreyt az m'hot tsurik arayngelozn in barak

00:27:10.402 --> 00:27:12.742
oder flegt geyn arbetn.

00:27:13.608 --> 00:27:16.365
nit geven vos ontsuton, m'iz gegangen ot ot

00:27:16.393 --> 00:27:17.754
in a hemd.

00:27:20.291 --> 00:27:22.243
s'iz nit geven vos tsu ton.

00:27:24.155 --> 00:27:30.054
a, a mantl hot men gedarft vartn az s'iz ver geshtorbn, me zol krign a mantl ontsuton.

00:27:30.213 --> 00:27:32.705
&lt;se&gt;, m'hot alts di zakhn tsugenumen.

00:27:32.981 --> 00:27:35.372
gehat eygene zakhn mit altsding.

00:27:40.288 --> 00:27:42.645
az ir zent aroys fun Shavl

00:27:42.819 --> 00:27:44.788
in fir un fertsik, yo?

00:27:44.287 --> 00:27:44.923
ye.

00:27:45.114 --> 00:27:47.049
far vos zent ir aroys?

00:27:48.033 --> 00:27:49.457
m'hot aykh aroys-

00:27:48.033 --> 00:27:50.400
in DACHAU hot men undz ge&lt;UNK&gt;.

00:27:49.457 --> 00:27:51.116
nor far vos?

00:27:51.577 --> 00:27:53.208
 ikh vey-

00:27:51.915 --> 00:27:55.133
zey hobn likvi-, hobn zey likvidirt Shavl?

00:27:55.728 --> 00:27:59.772
ye, zey hobn gedarft aroysgeyn, vayl di rusn zaynen shoyn geven

00:27:59.829 --> 00:28:03.148
mit di letste teg ver fun

00:28:03.390 --> 00:28:04.026
UNK

00:28:04.335 --> 00:28:09.663
&lt;zey&gt; voltn nit ge-, UNK, zey shteyen nokh eyn tog voltn mir bafrayt zikh dortn.
